Sources close to the counter-terrorism unit told the Sunday Times that Abdul Hadi Arwani , an opponent of Syrian President Bahsar Al-Assad had visited the area where he was killed with his son days before his death .
He was shot and killed in his car on a quiet street in North West London after being called to provide a quote for building work .
